00:36:44,560 --> 00:36:47,000
I think you just don't want to tire out
that person at home.

538
00:36:49,630 --> 00:36:52,000
By the way,
when you're back home for the New Year,

539
00:36:52,080 --> 00:36:54,870
did you tell your parents
that you're in a relationship?

540
00:36:56,430 --> 00:36:57,870
You should do it soon.

541
00:36:57,950 --> 00:37:00,200
See, our mum has all my messages.

542
00:37:00,280 --> 00:37:02,200
Shouldn't you leave a copy
of all his messages...

543
00:37:02,280 --> 00:37:04,000
with our parents?

544
00:37:05,000 --> 00:37:07,240
Since you're not going home,

545
00:37:07,320 --> 00:37:09,000
if anything happens,

546
00:37:09,080 --> 00:37:10,520
he would be a bigger suspect than I am.

547
00:37:10,600 --> 00:37:12,000
Suspect number one.

548
00:37:12,080 --> 00:37:13,720
Why can't you hope
for something good for me?

549
00:37:13,800 --> 00:37:15,520
Aren't I hoping
for something good for you now?

550
00:37:16,320 --> 00:37:18,120
Let's shop, buy clothes.

551
00:37:32,950 --> 00:37:34,320
What do you think? Do I look good?

552
00:37:36,000 --> 00:37:36,870
No.

553
00:37:37,800 --> 00:37:39,830
You can't even see,
but you're saying it doesn't look good.

554
00:37:44,800 --> 00:37:45,720
Nian Qin,

555
00:37:46,320 --> 00:37:49,000
are there no treatments for your eyes?

556
00:37:51,040 --> 00:37:52,110
No.

557
00:37:52,190 --> 00:37:53,240
It's congenital.

558
00:37:55,950 --> 00:37:57,830
Do you want my eyes to be cured so badly?

559
00:38:00,280 --> 00:38:02,000
Not really.

560
00:38:02,800 --> 00:38:05,680
But if you see what I look like,

561
00:38:05,760 --> 00:38:07,630
you might not date me.

562
00:38:09,430 --> 00:38:11,000
I know that you're a beautiful girl.

563
00:38:11,950 --> 00:38:13,000
How would you know?

564
00:38:13,470 --> 00:38:14,430
I can hear it.

565
00:38:16,950 --> 00:38:18,000
No.

566
00:38:19,800 --> 00:38:21,320
My beauty is incomparable.

567
00:38:23,600 --> 00:38:24,960
Think of it this way.

568
00:38:25,040 --> 00:38:26,830
If I'm not the prettiest,

569
00:38:26,910 --> 00:38:28,240
then I would be the cutest.

570
00:38:28,320 --> 00:38:30,200
If I'm not the cutest,

571
00:38:30,280 --> 00:38:31,820
then I would be the person
who loves you the most.

572
00:38:34,800 --> 00:38:35,830
Since you put it that way,

573
00:38:36,800 --> 00:38:38,480
now I really want to know...

574
00:38:39,230 --> 00:38:41,350
what the person who loves me the most
looks like.

575
00:38:50,150 --> 00:38:50,990
Come here.

576
00:38:52,910 --> 00:38:56,150
These are my eyebrows. They're messy.

577
00:38:56,230 --> 00:38:58,000
I don't really like to groom them.

578
00:38:59,910 --> 00:39:02,320
These are my eyes.

579
00:39:03,190 --> 00:39:06,000
I don't have a lot of lashes,

580
00:39:06,630 --> 00:39:09,110
and my eyes love to tear up,

581
00:39:09,190 --> 00:39:10,870
but my eyesight is perfect.

582
00:39:12,670 --> 00:39:13,910
This is my nose.

583
00:39:15,230 --> 00:39:16,150
It's small.

584
00:39:26,360 --> 00:39:29,960
I have to check to see if there are flaws,
so I can return you.

585
00:39:30,040 --> 00:39:31,150
You want to return me?

586
00:39:31,800 --> 00:39:32,670
No way.

587
00:39:36,150 --> 00:39:36,990
What's up?

588
00:39:43,800 --> 00:39:46,720
Everyone,
including us that are "normal..."

589
00:39:46,800 --> 00:39:48,440
would feel the anxiety that I mentioned...

590
00:39:48,520 --> 00:39:51,720
when interacting with people.

591
00:39:51,800 --> 00:39:54,240
The level of anxiety differs for everyone,

592
00:39:54,320 --> 00:39:55,720
and it's different based
on experience too.

593
00:39:55,800 --> 00:39:57,630
It's unavoidable.

594
00:39:57,710 --> 00:39:59,550
It's not something only you have,

595
00:39:59,630 --> 00:40:02,150
and it doesn't happen
because you're not good enough.

596
00:40:02,230 --> 00:40:05,550
The important thing is that you
should bravely open up your heart,

597
00:40:05,630 --> 00:40:07,150
bravely speak up,

598
00:40:07,230 --> 00:40:09,390
so that people know your thoughts.

599
00:40:09,470 --> 00:40:11,480
That way, you will find...

600
00:40:11,560 --> 00:40:13,590
that the possibilities in our future...

601
00:40:13,670 --> 00:40:16,000
are a lot more than we can imagine.

602
00:40:20,710 --> 00:40:22,760
Okay. That's the end of the lesson.

603
00:40:22,840 --> 00:40:23,680
Dismiss.

604
00:40:25,600 --> 00:40:26,440
All rise.

605
00:40:26,520 --> 00:40:29,520
Goodbye, Miss!

606
00:40:39,600 --> 00:40:40,720
Ms Sang.

607
00:40:42,910 --> 00:40:43,750
Xiao Wei.

608
00:40:44,230 --> 00:40:47,960
Xiao Ling told me
that she saw Mr Su before the class began.

609
00:40:48,040 --> 00:40:49,910
Did you invite him to listen in?

610
00:40:52,230 --> 00:40:53,520
I didn't know that.

611
00:40:53,600 --> 00:40:55,670
But thank you for letting me know.

612
00:40:56,360 --> 00:40:57,350
Go back to your seat.

613
00:41:06,550 --> 00:41:07,460
Let's see.

614
00:41:15,640 --> 00:41:18,220
Xiao Lu, did Nian Qin come to the school?

615
00:41:21,320 --> 00:41:22,240
Yes.

616
00:41:42,540 --> 00:41:44,620
(Sister)

617
00:41:46,280 --> 00:41:47,120
Hello?

618
00:41:50,230 --> 00:41:51,200
Okay.

619
00:41:51,630 --> 00:41:53,430
Please send the flight number to me.

620
00:41:54,120 --> 00:41:55,910
I'm going to start driving. Bye.

621
00:42:00,520 --> 00:42:02,830
Xiao Wei and Xiao Lu
were double witnesses.

622
00:42:02,910 --> 00:42:04,350
Don't deny it.

623
00:42:04,430 --> 00:42:05,630
You slipped away.

624
00:42:05,710 --> 00:42:07,000
You have to help me take a picture.

625
00:42:07,760 --> 00:42:09,680
How are these two things related?

626
00:42:09,760 --> 00:42:10,910
Of course they're related.

627
00:42:11,430 --> 00:42:12,720
You're my boyfriend,

628
00:42:12,800 --> 00:42:14,520
so you need to help me take pictures.

629
00:42:14,600 --> 00:42:15,870
Why do you need a photo?

630
00:42:16,800 --> 00:42:18,910
Because I dressed up differently today.

631
00:42:21,150 --> 00:42:22,590
Just push here later.

632
00:42:22,670 --> 00:42:25,280
Just push when I tell you to.

633
00:42:30,910 --> 00:42:31,750
Push.

634
00:42:35,040 --> 00:42:36,830
Push twice more.

635
00:42:37,320 --> 00:42:40,000
Don't you know that the secret
to taking pictures is to take two more?

636
00:42:45,600 --> 00:42:46,870
Push three more times.

637
00:42:51,430 --> 00:42:52,280
Then?

638
00:42:53,760 --> 00:42:54,630
Then...

639
00:42:56,120 --> 00:42:58,200
have we never taken a picture together?

640
00:42:58,280 --> 00:42:59,520
Let's take a picture together.

641
00:43:00,120 --> 00:43:00,960
Come here.

642
00:43:03,190 --> 00:43:04,800
Don't block, don't block.

643
00:43:07,430 --> 00:43:08,270
Here.

644
00:43:09,000 --> 00:43:11,320
You need to smile.
You look good when you smile.

645
00:43:12,320 --> 00:43:13,200
Look at the camera.

646
00:43:16,800 --> 00:43:17,910
Let me see.

647
00:43:18,430 --> 00:43:20,520
It looks quite good.

648
00:43:27,950 --> 00:43:28,960
Wait a moment.

649
00:43:31,120 --> 00:43:31,960
Hello?

650
00:43:33,040 --> 00:43:35,800
Wu Yan, why are you not home again?

651
00:43:36,360 --> 00:43:37,200
I...

652
00:43:37,950 --> 00:43:39,830
I have something going on in school.

653
00:43:39,910 --> 00:43:41,590
Come back at the end of the month.

654
00:43:41,670 --> 00:43:43,830
Your dad and I
have contacted a high school.

655
00:43:43,910 --> 00:43:46,110
They're looking for a psychology teacher.

656
00:43:46,190 --> 00:43:47,030
Mum...

657
00:43:47,560 --> 00:43:50,520
Bring your resume
and those certificates back.

658
00:43:50,600 --> 00:43:52,240
You need to prepare for it.

659
00:43:52,320 --> 00:43:53,430
There's an interview.

660
00:43:53,910 --> 00:43:55,440
It's inconvenient for me to discuss this
with you now.

661
00:43:55,520 --> 00:43:57,150
I can't talk now. Talk later.

662
00:43:57,230 --> 00:43:58,910
What do you mean inconvenient?

663
00:43:59,630 --> 00:44:01,390
Why have you been sneaking around lately?

664
00:44:01,470 --> 00:44:02,670
Okay, I'm hanging up. Bye bye.

665
00:44:06,040 --> 00:44:06,880
What's wrong?

666
00:44:09,280 --> 00:44:10,830
My mum called.

667
00:44:10,910 --> 00:44:13,200
She told me something about work.
